{{etyl|ang}} {{term|monandæg|mōnandæġ|day of the moon|lang=ang}}, from {{term|mona|mōna|moon|lang=ang}} + {{term|dæg||day|lang=ang}}, a [[calque]] of the {{etyl|la}} word {{term|dies lunae|lang=la}}

